### Internova Backend API Test Suite
### Production Base URL: https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app
### Health Check: GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/health
### Database Admin: https://pgweb-production-ad27.up.railway.app

### =============================================================================
### HEALTH CHECKS
### =============================================================================

### Health Check - Verify backend is running
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/health

### Application Info
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/info

### =============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Register a new STUDENT user
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teststudent@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "STUDENT",
  "studentIdNumber": "STU001",
  "departmentId": "uuid-here"
}

### Register a new COMPANY user
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testcompany@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "COMPANY_REP",
  "companyName": "Test Company Inc",
  "registrationNumber": "REG001",
  "industry": "Technology"
}

### Login (sets JWT cookie automatically)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teststudent@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Get current user profile (requires JWT cookie)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/me

### Refresh JWT token (requires JWT cookie)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/refresh

### Logout (clears JWT cookie)
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/auth/logout

### =============================================================================
### PUBLIC ENDPOINTS (No Authentication Required)
### =============================================================================

### Get all vacancies (public)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies?page=0&size=10

### Get single vacancy by ID (public)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/uuid-here

### Search vacancies (public)
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/search?keyword=developer&page=0&size=10

### =============================================================================
### STUDENT ENDPOINTS (Require JWT - STUDENT Role)
### =============================================================================

### Get student profile
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile

### Update student profile
PUT https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "course": "Computer Science",
  "cvUrl": "https://example.com/cv.pdf"
}

### Get profile completion status
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/students/profile-completion

### Get personalized vacancy feed for department
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/feed/department-uuid-here

### Apply to a vacancy
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vacancyId": "vacancy-uuid-here"
}

### Get my applications
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications?page=0&size=10

### Get single application
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/application-uuid-here

### Withdraw application
DELETE https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/application-uuid-here

### Submit logbook entry
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/submit?date=2024-03-19
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Worked on implementing authentication module using Spring Security and JWT tokens.",
  "tags": "authentication,spring-boot,jwt,security"
}

### Get my logbook entries
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/my-logs

### =============================================================================
### COMPANY ENDPOINTS (Require JWT - COMPANY_REP Role)
### =============================================================================

### Get company profile
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/profile

### Get company's posted vacancies
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/vacancies

### Post new vacancy
POST https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Software Developer Intern",
  "description": "Great opportunity for CS students to work on real projects.",
  "requirements": "Java, Spring Boot knowledge preferred. Git experience required.",
  "location": "Remote"
}

### Update vacancy
PUT https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/vacancies/vacancy-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "requirements": "Updated requirements"
}

### Update application status
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications/application-uuid-here/status?status=ACCEPTED

### Get verification status
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/company/verification-status

### =============================================================================
### NOTIFICATION ENDPOINTS (Require JWT - Any Authenticated User)
### =============================================================================

### Get my notifications
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=10

### Get unread notification count
GET https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/unread/count

### Mark notification as read
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/notification-uuid-here/read

### Mark all notifications as read
PATCH https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications/read-all

### =============================================================================
### TESTING WORKFLOW
### =============================================================================
# 1. Check health: GET /actuator/health
# 2. Register users: POST /api/v1/auth/register (student + company)
# 3. Login: POST /api/v1/auth/login (get JWT cookie)
# 4. Test public endpoints: GET /api/v1/vacancies
# 5. Test role-specific endpoints with appropriate JWT
# 6. Test complete flows: Apply to vacancy, submit logs, etc.

### =============================================================================
### ERROR CODES REFERENCE
### =============================================================================
# 200: Success
# 400: Bad Request (validation error)
# 401: Unauthorized (missing/invalid JWT)
# 403: Forbidden (insufficient permissions)
# 404: Not Found
# 500: Internal Server Error

### =============================================================================
### IMPORTANT NOTES
### =============================================================================
# - JWT tokens are stored in HttpOnly cookies automatically
# - Cookies are sent automatically with requests (withCredentials: true in frontend)
# - All authenticated endpoints require valid JWT in cookie
# - Student endpoints require STUDENT role, Company endpoints require COMPANY_REP role
# - Public endpoints work without authentication
# - Database must have departments/universities for registration to work

### Get my applications (PowerShell - requires JWT, student role)
# Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/applications?page=0&size=10" -Method GET -Headers @{"Cookie"="JWT=your-jwt-token-here"}

### =============================================================================
### LOGBOOK ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Submit log entry (PowerShell - requires JWT, student role)
# Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/submit?date=2024-03-19" -Method POST -ContentType "application/json" -Headers @{"Cookie"="JWT=your-jwt-token-here"} -Body '{"content":"Worked on Spring Boot project, implemented authentication","tags":"spring-boot,authentication,java"}'

### Get my log entries (PowerShell - requires JWT, student role)
# Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/logbooks/my-logs" -Method GET -Headers @{"Cookie"="JWT=your-jwt-token-here"}

### =============================================================================
### NOTIFICATION ENDPOINTS
### =============================================================================

### Get my notifications (PowerShell - requires JWT)
# Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/api/v1/notifications?page=0&size=10" -Method GET -Headers @{"Cookie"="JWT=your-jwt-token-here"}

### =============================================================================
### TESTING WORKFLOW
### =============================================================================
# 1. Test health: Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "https://internova-backend-production.up.railway.app/actuator/health" -Method GET
# 2. Register a user: Use the register command above
# 3. Login: Use the login command above (save the JWT from response cookies)
# 4. Test authenticated endpoints: Use the JWT in Cookie header
# 5. Test role-specific endpoints based on user type registered